-- pd.package: floating Banner
name: fastn-community.github.io/banner

`floating-banner` is another banner component which have `link` as parameter,
which will take user to the link value.

Use our `floating-banner` on your fastn web projects where you would like to add
click to action for your web page users.

🌟 Ex.g. Look at the top of this page.

To use floating-banner on your `FTD` web pages, add below `fastn` dependency
into `FASTN.ftd` file:

-- ft.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fastn.dependency: fastn-community.github.io/banner
\-- fastn.auto-import: fastn-community.github.io/banner

-- tf.markdown:

Once you add above lines into your `fastn` package, add `banner` into your
`.ftd` files:

-- cb.rendered:

-- cb.rendered.input:

\-- banner.floating-banner: 
link: https://github.com/fastn-stack/fastn/ 

Star on GitHub ⭐

-- cb.rendered.output:

-- banner.floating-banner: 
link: https://github.com/fastn-stack/fastn/ 

Star on GitHub ⭐

-- end: cb.rendered.output

